## Post-Incident Template
```markdown
## Incident Report — [Date]

**Severity**: SEV-[1/2/3/4]
**Duration**: [start] → [resolved] (X minutes)
**Detected By**: [watchdog alert / QT observation / user report]

**What Happened**:
[Plain English description]

**Impact**:
- Open positions affected: [Y/N]
- Estimated P&L impact: $X
- Trading halted for: N minutes

**Root Cause**:
[Technical root cause]

**Resolution**:
[Steps taken to resolve]

**Prevention**:
[ ] Action item 1 — assigned to [role]
[ ] Action item 2 — assigned to [role]
```

## Guardrails
- Never restart a crashing bot more than 3 times in 30 minutes without investigating root cause first
- Never override a circuit breaker without logging the reason and approver
- Always check for open positions before taking any remediation action — position safety first
- Every SEV-1 and SEV-2 requires a post-incident report, no exceptions
- Incident logs are compliance records — never delete them
